<view class="page safe-bottom">
  <view class="about-header">
    <view class="about-logo">
      <image src="/assets/logo-study-record-mini.png" mode="aspectFit" style="width: 128rpx; height: 128rpx;" />
    </view>
    <view class="about-name">作业用餐小记</view>
    <view class="about-version">v{{version}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-header">
      <text class="section-title">系统信息</text>
    </view>
    <van-cell-group>
      <van-cell title="系统名称" value="作业用餐小记" />
    </van-cell-group>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-header">
      <text class="section-title">隐私政策</text>
    </view>
    <view class="about-policy">
      本系统仅在账号登录、记录查询、资料维护和图片上传所需范围内处理用户信息，不会在未经授权的情况下向第三方披露个人信息。
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
